SimplifiedChinese.example:
printf("samples: 1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")
或
printf("1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")

- 注意：FireWater遇到换行才会打印数据，很多新用户在这里产生疑惑。

TraditionalChinese.example:
printf("samples: 1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")
或
printf("1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")

- 注意：FireWater遇到換行才會列印數據，很多新用戶在這裡產生疑惑。

English.example:
printf("samples: 1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")
Or
printf("1.1, 3.2, -0.6, -0.9\n")

- Note: FireWater will print data only when it encounters a line break. Many new users have doubts here.
